Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: bachata
Version: 0.1
Summary: Bachata is a chat server toolkit on top of asyncio and Tornado.
Home-page: https://github.com/05bit/bachata
Author: Alexey Kinev
Author-email: rudy@05bit.com
License: Apache
Description: **Bachata** is a chat server toolkit on top of `asyncio`_ and `Tornado`_.
        
        .. _Tornado: http://www.tornadoweb.org/en/stable/
        .. _asyncio: https://docs.python.org/3.4/library/asyncio.html
        
        Overview
        --------
        
        - Requires Python 3.3+
        - Requires Tornado running on asyncio event loop
        - Implements simple messages queue on Redis LPUSH / BRPOP
        - Implements reliable messages delivery on Redis BRPOPLPUSH pattern
        - JSON messages format
        - Custom messages routing
        
        
